summary: This is just the blender model. If someone could please download it and texture it and do whatever could you please and then give me some credit for making it. Much appreciated :D
descriptionHtml:
This is just a small sword mod I made but considering i am probably the crappiest person at texturing something i decided to upload it to the nexus and see what happened. 

All it includes is the blend file for the sword. If you can make the model better feel free to do whatever you want just remember some credit towards me for the actual model. 

If you do make a better one [b][color=red]can you please upload your images of it to this page[/color][/b]
author: sshep58
